item.description: Come to Harvard Square for trivia and a pretty extensive and good selection of sandwiches, fries, et al.Â Flavors of Shipyard I haven't had? Yes please. It is possible but time-consuming to get a parking space in this area. Public transit is often a better option. I'll be there by 7:30 and would be pleased if people can arrive pre-game to talk and help hold the table down. Trivia starts at 8. This is likely to be the only meetup I can host in May so let's see some peeps here.
